---
title: Mumbai Lentil & Beef Kumara Dosa-Dillas with Charred Corn Salsa & Yoghurt
description: These chunky, veggie-packed dosa-dillas are the ultimate ruler of the dinner table. So bow down to the might of the roasted
kumara and lentils, cooked in rich spices and accompanied by a charred corn salsa. Long may this tasty dish reign.

